qas.question: Which newspaper is the most produced through the state of Oklahoma?
What is the name of The Oklahoman's website?
What is Oklahoma Cities daily business newspaper?

context: <a0_0>The Oklahoman<a0_0/> is Oklahoma City's major daily newspaper and is the most widely circulated in the state. <a1_0>NewsOK.com<a1_0/> is the Oklahoman's online presence. <a2_0>Oklahoma Gazette<a2_0/> is Oklahoma City's independent newsweekly, featuring such staples as local commentary, feature stories, restaurant reviews and movie listings and music and entertainment. <a3_0>The Journal Record<a3_0/> is the city's daily business newspaper and okcBIZ is a monthly publication that covers business news affecting those who live and work in Central Oklahoma.
